collection.title: Welcome to SnowX, the first NFT marketplace in VR
collection.creator: SnowX and Hiyoko Shisho

artworks.title: SnowX NFT
artworks.description:
Welcome to SnowX!
Take home this NFT as a memento of your first experience with SnowX.
This logo was drawn by VR artist Hiyoko Shisho and won the SnowX logo competition.
If you look closely, you can see the letter X is hidden.
